148
00:15:53,036 --> 00:15:56,873
In the top left drawer rests a key.

149
00:15:56,956 --> 00:16:00,960
That key opens the compartment
which contains the List.

150
00:16:01,002 --> 00:16:03,672
By now there should be
a letter on my desk...

151
00:16:03,755 --> 00:16:07,926
