179
00:18:08,672 --> 00:18:10,340
I can give you a lift.

180
00:18:10,423 --> 00:18:15,679
Or at least allow me to wait with you,
make sure everything's okay.

181
00:18:15,762 --> 00:18:18,098
Really, it's okay.
I think I'll just chance it with Harold.

182
00:18:18,139 --> 00:18:21,351
How 'bout, uh, I buy you lunch?

183
00:18:21,434 --> 00:18:25,188
Hey, uh-
Y'all can call my cell, right?

184
00:18:25,271 --> 00:18:27,732
- Yeah.
- How's that barbecue over there?

185
00:18:27,816 --> 00:18:31,528
The best pig in the county. Tell 'em I sent you,
they'll give you extra hush puppies.

186
00:18:31,611 --> 00:18:35,573
- Best pig in the whole county.
- Sugar, you sure you don't want a ride?

187
00:18:35,657 --> 00:18:38,702
We'll be in plain view
the whole way.

188
00:18:40,537 --> 00:18:42,539
Promise.

189
00:18:44,791 --> 00:18:46,710
Renny Jacobson.

190
00:18:48,211 --> 00:18:50,171
Jo Johnston.

191
00:18:51,631 --> 00:18:53,550
Pleased to meet you, Jo.

192
00:18:53,633 --> 00:18:56,970
