00:19:07,564 --> 00:19:09,566
I always thank God for barbecue.

194
00:19:09,649 --> 00:19:12,360
At this place,
you pray after you eat.

195
00:19:15,155 --> 00:19:18,908
- Some more tea?
- Yeah. Please.

196
00:19:18,992 --> 00:19:22,871
Mmm. Thank you.

197
00:19:24,706 --> 00:19:28,168
- What was your father's name?
- Taylor.

198
00:19:28,251 --> 00:19:31,004
Taylor Johnston.

199
00:19:31,046 --> 00:19:34,215
Harold.

200
00:19:34,299 --> 00:19:37,677
Ooh. Thanks. Hello.

201
00:19:41,431 --> 00:19:43,391
Mm-hmm.

202
00:19:45,602 --> 00:19:47,562
Okay. Yeah.

203
00:19:51,191 --> 00:19:54,736
Thank you. Yeah. Okay. Bye.

