the Rice Planter's Inn?

206
00:20:06,373 --> 00:20:09,542
Jo Taylor Johnston?

207
00:20:11,169 --> 00:20:13,088
Yeah.

208
00:20:13,171 --> 00:20:17,842
Josiah Fletchall Jacobson.

209
