239
00:22:33,186 --> 00:22:37,649
Novels, for sure, by Faulkner, Percy.

240
00:22:37,732 --> 00:22:40,527
Characters so real,
they remind me of my neighbors.

241
00:22:42,612 --> 00:22:45,699
The sun rising over
the Ashley River...

242
00:22:45,740 --> 00:22:47,909
