comin' off the water.

243
00:22:49,577 --> 00:22:53,373
- And barbecue.
- Definitely the barbecue.

244
00:22:53,456 --> 00:22:55,583
Wow.

245
00:22:55,667 --> 00:22:58,294
Impressive, huh?

246
00:22:58,378 --> 00:23:01,256
- You ready for this, Jo?
- I guess.

247
